Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.84,0:00:03.86,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Oh wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.15,0:00:04.94,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Oh my gosh!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.68,0:00:09.06,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Oh my gosh oh my gosh oh my gosh oh my gosh!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.27,0:00:11.60,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Oh my gosh oh my gosh oh my gosh!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.60,0:00:12.54,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Applejack!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.47,0:00:18.08,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Twilight, Twilight, where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.36,0:00:19.47,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I'm in here, Pinkie!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.48,0:00:20.24,Twilight,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.55,0:00:22.52,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,You'll never guess what I just got!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.82,0:00:23.85,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Is everything okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.52,0:00:26.02,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,We heard a lot of oh my goshin',
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.11,0:00:28.40,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,and we weren't sure if it was a good thing or a bad thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.74,0:00:29.90,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,A good thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.09,0:00:33.62,Twilight,,0,0,0,,"To pink pony who lives with baked goods."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.90,0:00:35.28,Twilight,,0,0,0,,It's from the yaks!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.34,0:00:39.40,Twilight,,0,0,0,,"Yaks cordially invite pink pony to
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.46,0:00:40.79,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Come. Now."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.20,0:00:43.61,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Prince Rutherford is officially inviting me
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.61,0:00:45.76,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,to the Yakslurbertfest in Yakyakistan!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.90,0:00:48.28,Rarity,,0,0,0,,What is Yakslubertfest?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.52,0:00:50.39,Twilight,,0,0,0,,It's a sacred yak holiday.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.42,0:00:53.31,Twilight,,0,0,0,,How did you get Prince Rutherford to invite you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.31,0:00:56.96,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,I subtly hinted for an invitation in my letters to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.58,0:01:00.62,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,"May I please come to Yakslurbertfest?"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.65,0:01:01.60,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,"Pretty please?"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.21,0:01:02.89,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,"Pretty please?"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.06,0:01:03.80,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,"Pretty please?"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.80,0:01:06.12,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,"Pretty-pretty-pretty-pretty-pretty please?"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.60,0:01:09.05,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,After my seventeenth scroll,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.05,0:01:11.60,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,I think he picked up what I was putting down.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.00,0:01:58.83,Twilight,,0,0,0,,You know, we still don't know a lot about the yaks.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.95,0:02:02.64,Twilight,,0,0,0,,So I think you should definitely go to Yakslurbertfest, Pinkie.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.73,0:02:03.55,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.97,0:02:06.82,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Fostering friendships is what ponies do.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.82,0:02:08.19,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,I won't let you down!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.19,0:02:09.56,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,It's an honor to be the
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.56,0:02:13.15,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,official friendship ambassador to the yaks!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.93,0:02:15.97,Twilight,,0,0,0,,That's not an official position.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.65,0:02:17.53,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.53,0:02:18.88,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,You're the Princess of Friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.99,0:02:21.13,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,You can make it happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.69,0:02:24.12,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Okay, you got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.93,0:02:26.87,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,You have to make it official!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.23,0:02:29.08,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.20,0:02:30.83,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I hereby make Pinkie Pie
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.83,0:02:33.45,Twilight,,0,0,0,,the official friendship ambassador to the yaks!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.29,0:02:39.19,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,This is officially…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.27,0:02:41.35,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,the most exciting day in my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.52,0:02:47.67,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Yoohoo, Gummy, pay attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.67,0:02:51.35,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,We're in the middle of an official friendship ambassador road trip game.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.04,0:02:54.76,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,That's better.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.89,0:02:55.24,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.35,0:02:57.53,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,I spy with my official friendship eye…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.53,0:02:58.93,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,something that is blue!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.33,0:03:08.49,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,We're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.24,0:03:12.41,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Oh, by the way,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.41,0:03:13.91,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,the answer was sky!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.12,0:03:14.73,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,I win!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.63,0:03:18.96,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I know that was a hard one, Gummy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.35,0:03:22.61,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,You're the best official friendship travel companion ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.03,0:03:29.88,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,What is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.00,0:03:33.65,Rutherford,,0,0,0,,Yaks destroy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.95,0:03:35.72,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Yaks destroy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.32,0:03:37.16,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Yikes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.16,0:03:40.44,Rutherford,,0,0,0,,Pink pony!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.71,0:03:43.12,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,It's an honor to…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.71,0:03:45.24,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,be here, Prince.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.85,0:03:47.48,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Did something terrible happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.71,0:03:49.91,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Is canceled?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.23,0:03:51.09,Rutherford,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.19,0:03:52.72,Rutherford,,0,0,0,,This's Yakslurbertfest.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.88,0:03:55.16,Rutherford,,0,0,0,,Where yaks get together to stomp!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.37,0:03:59.60,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,I didn't know that was part of the sacred holiday.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.60,0:04:02.84,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,So this angry display of destruction is part of the festivities?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.84,0:04:05.84,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,And here I thought you yaks were just in a bad mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.84,0:04:06.75,Rutherford,,0,0,0,,No-o-o.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.79,0:04:09.25,Rutherford,,0,0,0,,Stomping relaxes yaks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.35,0:04:15.99,Rutherford,,0,0,0,,Yaks had never been so clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.96,0:04:19.67,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,This is awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.32,0:04:26.05,Rutherford,,0,0,0,,Sto-op!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.81,0:04:32.17,Rutherford,,0,0,0,,Pink pony better check self before wreck self.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.60,0:04:36.24,Rutherford,,0,0,0,,That is century old sacred yak twig
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.24,0:04:39.98,Rutherford,,0,0,0,,passed down from generation to generation.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.01,0:04:41.87,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.95,0:04:43.35,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.55,0:04:46.56,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,I was just trying to get into the spirit of Yakslerberfest.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.48,0:04:48.39,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Maybe I can fix it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.24,0:04:53.53,Rutherford,,0,0,0,,Yak kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.68,0:05:00.68,Rutherford,,0,0,0,,Yak got pink pony good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.76,0:05:02.28,Rutherford,,0,0,0,,Horn bump!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.49,0:05:07.76,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Oh, you sure did, Prince Rutherford.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.71,0:05:10.51,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,That was a close one, Gummy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.51,0:05:12.81,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,This trip has to be perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.81,0:05:15.07,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,After all, we're not just visiting as friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.07,0:05:18.25,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,We are on official friendship ambassador business!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.32,0:05:21.52,Rutherford,,0,0,0,,Less talking! More stomping!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.93,0:05:23.67,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.63,0:05:27.13,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,A-and stompy, stompy, stompy, stompy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.05,0:05:32.71,Rutherford,,0,0,0,,Now I take pink pony on Yakyakistan tour.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.84,0:05:34.28,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Thanks Prince Rutherford, but
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.40,0:05:36.32,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,I've been to Yakyakistan before.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.41,0:05:38.73,Rutherford,,0,0,0,,Yak know, but thought pink pony
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.73,0:05:43.09,Rutherford,,0,0,0,,might not recognize town since decorated for Yakflerbertfest.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.43,0:05:44.99,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.99,0:05:47.71,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,It's so different now that you've pointed it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.31,0:05:51.03,Rutherford,,0,0,0,,Oh, yaks not just have eye for decorating.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.24,0:05:53.99,Rutherford,,0,0,0,,Yaks also amazing builders!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.12,0:05:56.11,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,No. Way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.27,0:05:59.76,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,I thought you hired professional contractors.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.81,0:06:01.28,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.45,0:06:02.39,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Let me help you with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.22,0:06:08.97,Rutherford,,0,0,0,,This ceremonial yak's fire pit,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.16,0:06:10.93,Rutherford,,0,0,0,,where yaks tell stories.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.51,0:06:16.33,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,I have so much to officially tell the ponies when I get back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.34,0:06:19.01,Rutherford,,0,0,0,,This yak eating hut.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.10,0:06:20.61,Rutherford,,0,0,0,,Hut, where yaks eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.16,0:06:26.49,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,The perfect balance of vanilla extract.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.64,0:06:28.85,Rutherford,,0,0,0,,Yaks grow own vanilla bean.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.93,0:06:30.30,Rutherford,,0,0,0,,Nothing important.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.69,0:06:41.90,Rutherford,,0,0,0,,Yak sleeping hut.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.06,0:06:43.77,Rutherford,,0,0,0,,Hut, where yaks sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.63,0:06:54.13,Rutherford,,0,0,0,,Yak music hut.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.13,0:06:57.57,Rutherford,,0,0,0,,Hut, where yaks enjoy beautiful music.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.42,0:07:01.12,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,This is beautiful and…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.99,0:07:04.28,Rutherford,,0,0,0,,Pink pony ruin with talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.40,0:07:11.88,Rutherford,,0,0,0,,And that how yaks defeat evil and save world.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.09,0:07:16.45,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Pink pony like yak story.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.27,0:07:18.58,Rutherford,,0,0,0,,Yak impressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.74,0:07:22.03,Rutherford,,0,0,0,,Pink pony can almost be honorary yak.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.05,0:07:25.44,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Official friendship ambassador and honorary yak?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.01,0:07:28.33,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Pink pony's title card is full!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.72,0:07:29.69,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Horn bump?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.90,0:07:31.57,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Oh, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.57,0:07:32.65,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,I don't have a horn.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.34,0:07:37.40,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Prince Rutherford, can I get some honorary yak's horns?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.52,0:07:40.85,Rutherford,,0,0,0,,No. Yak horn too heavy for small pony head.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.77,0:07:46.05,Rutherford,,0,0,0,,Yakslerberfest stomp time!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.49,0:07:54.69,Rutherford,,0,0,0,,Stomp harder!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.75,0:07:56.45,Rutherford,,0,0,0,,Yaks extra happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.45,0:07:58.11,Rutherford,,0,0,0,,Ponies and yaks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.15,0:07:58.77,Rutherford,,0,0,0,,Friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.52,0:08:15.71,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Is this part of the festival?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.43,0:08:18.65,Rutherford,,0,0,0,,Pink pony ask too many questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.66,0:08:27.39,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Everything is buried in snow!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.01,0:08:29.57,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,What are we gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.75,0:08:31.86,Rutherford,,0,0,0,,Yaks fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.89,0:08:34.07,Rutherford,,0,0,0,,Snow fall from mountains all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.62,0:08:35.50,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,All the time?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.94,0:08:37.86,Rutherford,,0,0,0,,Every Yakslerberfest.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.86,0:08:38.37,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.51,0:08:43.24,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Avalanches like this completely bury all of your homes every Yakslerberfest?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.43,0:08:44.06,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.37,0:08:47.22,Rutherford,,0,0,0,,This is big avalanche.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.49,0:08:48.82,Rutherford,,0,0,0,,But not a problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.82,0:08:50.13,Rutherford,,0,0,0,,For yaks are tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.33,0:08:52.13,Rutherford,,0,0,0,,Yaks dig through snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.21,0:08:53.34,Rutherford,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't take long.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.81,0:08:54.87,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Oh good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.87,0:08:56.73,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,You have an emergency plan in place.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.34,0:09:01.58,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Here, let me help.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.95,0:09:13.17,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,I'm tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.31,0:09:14.79,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,We must be almost done.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.58,0:09:18.03,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,There's still snow everywhere?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.25,0:09:20.50,Rutherford,,0,0,0,,Yaks keep digging.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.11,0:09:33.53,Rutherford,,0,0,0,,Yaks stop digging.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.53,0:09:34.99,Rutherford,,0,0,0,,Make situation worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.65,0:09:36.11,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.38,0:09:37.98,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, Prince Rutherford.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.05,0:09:40.17,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,I'll go back to Ponyville and ask for help.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.26,0:09:43.54,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Twilight and the others will be happy to come dig the snow away.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.63,0:09:46.89,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,After all, many hooves make light work.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.99,0:09:47.73,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Right, Gummy?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.19,0:09:50.35,Rutherford,,0,0,0,,Yaks no need pony help!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.75,0:09:55.70,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Why I'm sure it'll be okay,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.70,0:09:57.31,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,'cause you probably have a plan B.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.37,0:09:57.99,Rutherford,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.38,0:10:00.29,Rutherford,,0,0,0,,Yaks wait for snow to melt.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.83,0:10:02.61,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,All this snow?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.81,0:10:05.86,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,It'll take a thousand moons before it melts!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.86,0:10:07.86,Rutherford,,0,0,0,,Yaks known for their patience.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.14,0:10:10.54,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Well… be that as it may.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.54,0:10:12.28,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,In the meantime what will you eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.28,0:10:13.86,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Where will you sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.25,0:10:15.99,Rutherford,,0,0,0,,Yaks can make this work.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.99,0:10:19.24,Rutherford,,0,0,0,,Hardship make yaks the strong yaks that yaks are.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.24,0:10:21.06,Rutherford,,0,0,0,,If pink pony disagrees,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.06,0:10:23.13,Rutherford,,0,0,0,,than she can leave Yakyakistan
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.13,0:10:24.72,Rutherford,,0,0,0,,and never return!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.93,0:10:28.56,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Of course pink pony agrees with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.56,0:10:31.46,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Hey, let's try out some snow recipes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.05,0:10:35.99,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Snow cakes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.29,0:10:37.39,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Snow spaghetti!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.54,0:10:39.03,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Snow sandwiches!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.69,0:10:43.73,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Yaks can make this work.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.08,0:10:49.39,Rutherford,,0,0,0,,Yak tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.39,0:10:51.84,Rutherford,,0,0,0,,Yak retire to new sleeping hut.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.37,0:11:09.99,Rutherford,,0,0,0,,Snow cake good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.99,0:11:18.25,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Just the right balance of cold and water.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.21,0:11:22.05,Rutherford,,0,0,0,,Stop! Yak eating new eating hut!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.61,0:11:28.90,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Prince Rutherford, what are we doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.90,0:11:31.79,Rutherford,,0,0,0,,It's obvious. This new music hut.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.79,0:11:35.03,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Oh, so we're swaying to…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.21,0:11:37.97,Rutherford,,0,0,0,,Shhh! Pink pony ruins snow music with talking!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.17,0:11:45.58,SomeponyYellow,,0,0,0,,What was yak?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.58,0:11:48.83,SomeponyBlueOnYellow,,0,0,0,,Yak stomach rumbles. Yak hungry!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.65,0:11:51.50,SomeponyYellow,,0,0,0,,Shh! Prince yak will hear yak!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.63,0:11:54.32,SomeponyBlueOnYellow,,0,0,0,,But snow worse than yak ever seen!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.32,0:11:57.27,SomeponyYellow,,0,0,0,,Yak know. Yak hungry too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.19,0:11:59.71,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Gummy, did you hear that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.71,0:12:01.70,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,They can't make it work!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.57,0:12:04.96,Rutherford,,0,0,0,,Yaks stop swaying!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.96,0:12:06.14,Rutherford,,0,0,0,,Music over!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.35,0:12:09.35,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,If Twilight and the others knew what was going on,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.35,0:12:11.01,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,they would be here to help in a pony's heartbeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.01,0:12:14.68,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Have to convince Prince Rutherford that asking to help is okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.68,0:12:15.97,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Would you help me Gummy?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.91,0:12:17.69,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.69,0:12:21.07,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,And see, asking you to help wasn't in hard at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.68,0:12:28.77,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Pink Pony has gathered you around a new ceremonial yak firepit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.01,0:12:30.59,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,To tell you a story.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.59,0:12:32.58,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,A yak tradition, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.49,0:12:35.38,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.65,0:12:38.53,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,This is a story about a group of…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.74,0:12:39.94,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,the goats.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.94,0:12:42.10,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Who live in the desert.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.27,0:12:43.98,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,There was a sandstorm
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.98,0:12:46.89,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,and there entire village was buried in sand.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.89,0:12:49.05,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,There was nothing they could do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.05,0:12:53.73,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,They knew, they could not survive by only eating sand-wiches.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.18,0:12:55.01,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.14,0:12:58.66,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Okay, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.91,0:13:02.33,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Finally the goat's brave wise leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.33,0:13:06.79,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Let's just call him Prince… Drutherford.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.79,0:13:09.17,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Decides that they couldn't to it by themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.17,0:13:11.92,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,So he asked the neighboring town of the…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.92,0:13:13.76,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Bovineville to come help them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.97,0:13:15.47,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Yeah, cows!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.47,0:13:19.64,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,The magical cows helped the goats,\Neveryone survived and lived happily ever after.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.64,0:13:22.70,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Because they asked for help.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.21,0:13:23.89,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,The end!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.12,0:13:29.47,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,So what is the moral of that story?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.47,0:13:32.43,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Is it "A" — asking for help is okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.43,0:13:35.73,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,"B" — asking for help saves the day?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.73,0:13:39.79,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Or "C" — asking for help is good for everypony?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.79,0:13:41.79,Rutherford,,0,0,0,,"D" — goats weak and horrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.79,0:13:45.03,Rutherford,,0,0,0,,Magic bovines need to stay out of goats' business!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.91,0:13:48.13,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Not quite.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.35,0:13:51.21,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Any yak wanna shout out another answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.02,0:14:02.13,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Hey Prince Rutherford, I wanna talk to you about something…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.13,0:14:03.98,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Uh, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.98,0:14:07.71,Rutherford,,0,0,0,,Yak's snowbed got a little melty last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.25,0:14:09.70,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Okay, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.70,0:14:11.91,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,That's what I wanna talk to you about.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.91,0:14:12.86,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,You know,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.86,0:14:16.06,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,these yak's snowbeds are the fluffiest I ever slept in.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.06,0:14:19.36,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,They so comfortable you forget what it's just a cold block of ice.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.36,0:14:20.95,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,And the yak's snow sandwiches.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.31,0:14:26.21,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,I hate it when food burns your mouth and overwhelms it with flavor.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.34,0:14:28.74,Rutherford,,0,0,0,,Oh. Yak hates that too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.99,0:14:32.79,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,You know who would really really enjoy these snow sandwiches?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.79,0:14:35.24,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Twilight Sparkle and the other ponies!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.75,0:14:38.29,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Hey. I have an idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.78,0:14:42.11,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Why don't I go to Ponyville and bring them back here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.11,0:14:44.24,Rutherford,,0,0,0,,Ponies like snow sandwich?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.24,0:14:46.72,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Oh, ponies love snow sandwiches!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.72,0:14:50.22,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,And hey, while they're here, you can ask if they'll clear the snow away.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.22,0:14:51.57,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Fun, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.30,0:14:54.48,Rutherford,,0,0,0,,When Prince was little yak,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.80,0:14:57.01,Rutherford,,0,0,0,,Prince stomped on ground too hard,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.33,0:14:59.88,Rutherford,,0,0,0,,made deep hole and fell into hole.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.15,0:15:02.31,Rutherford,,0,0,0,,Ice froze over hole.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.31,0:15:06.42,Rutherford,,0,0,0,,Prince waved to friends and family from inside frozen hole.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.66,0:15:08.56,Rutherford,,0,0,0,,Waited for spring thaw.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.56,0:15:10.96,Rutherford,,0,0,0,,Prince survived on own.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.12,0:15:12.40,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.40,0:15:14.97,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,You spent the whole winter in a hole?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.97,0:15:15.87,Rutherford,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.87,0:15:17.75,Rutherford,,0,0,0,,And yak never asked for help.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.83,0:15:20.56,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.79,0:15:23.86,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,First of all, how did you make such deep hole from stomping?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.86,0:15:26.05,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,And how did it freeze over so fast?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.05,0:15:29.61,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,And how could you see your family and friends to wave to them from inside frozen hole?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.61,0:15:32.92,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Even if all that was possible, how did you breathe in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.73,0:15:36.06,Rutherford,,0,0,0,,Yaks don't ask for help!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.34,0:15:39.00,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,But the yaks are hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.00,0:15:41.25,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,And who knows when the snow might melt.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.25,0:15:42.62,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,I just don't understand why…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.62,0:15:43.54,Rutherford,,0,0,0,,Oh yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.54,0:15:47.64,Rutherford,,0,0,0,,It's clear now that pink pony does not understand yaks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.83,0:15:50.54,Rutherford,,0,0,0,,Honorary yak status… rescinded.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.52,0:15:54.73,Rutherford,,0,0,0,,Bang! Pretend there's door.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.73,0:15:56.58,Rutherford,,0,0,0,,I just slammed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.71,0:15:59.73,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Fine! Be stubborn!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.56,0:16:08.16,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Oh, those yaks are so stubborn!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.16,0:16:10.85,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,They refuse to ask for help even though they need it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.85,0:16:15.11,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Well, this official friendship ambassador is gonna take matters into her own hooves.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.11,0:16:16.53,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,I'll show them!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.74,0:16:21.57,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,You're right, Gummy, I am too worked up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.57,0:16:24.71,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Roadtrip game would officially calm me down.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.96,0:16:28.11,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,I know! Let's play "Twenty million questions".
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.11,0:16:29.21,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,You think of something,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.21,0:16:33.46,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,then I'll ask you twenty million questions until I can come up with what you're thinking of.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.46,0:16:34.13,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.13,0:16:34.88,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Is it blue?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.88,0:16:35.63,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Is it green?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.63,0:16:36.18,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Is it red?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.18,0:16:37.15,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Is it greenish red?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.15,0:16:38.17,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Is it reddish blue?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.17,0:16:39.45,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Is it bigger than a breadbox?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.45,0:16:40.73,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Is it smaller than a breadbox?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.73,0:16:41.69,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Is it a breadbox?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.69,0:16:42.70,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Is it bread?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.70,0:16:43.42,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Is it tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.42,0:16:45.30,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Is it Granny Smith dentures?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.30,0:16:46.58,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Is it you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.58,0:16:47.44,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Is it a rooster?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.44,0:16:48.59,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Is it a red rooster?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.59,0:16:50.43,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Is it a red rooster eating corn?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.30,0:16:53.39,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Used up all twenty million questions!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.39,0:16:55.09,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Oh well, we are here anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.95,0:17:01.48,Rutherford,,0,0,0,,Official pony balloon still here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.99,0:17:07.20,Rutherford,,0,0,0,,Pink pony gone, because pink pony not tough like yaks.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.39,0:17:10.09,Rutherford,,0,0,0,,Horn bump in agreement!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.09,0:17:10.96,Rutherford,,0,0,0,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.03,0:17:19.24,Rutherford,,0,0,0,,Snow sandwich lose novelty.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.24,0:17:21.16,Rutherford,,0,0,0,,Snow couscous for dinner!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.61,0:17:25.39,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Then Prince Rutherford said:
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.39,0:17:27.57,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,"Bang! Pretend there is door.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.57,0:17:29.40,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,I just slammed it."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.40,0:17:30.12,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Pinkie Pie…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.12,0:17:31.72,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,So then pink pony said:
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.72,0:17:33.75,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,"Fine! Be stubborn!"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.05,0:17:36.71,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Pinkie Pie, we have to help the yaks!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.71,0:17:38.26,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,So, in conclusion,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.26,0:17:40.35,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,we have to help the yaks!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.49,0:17:43.26,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Just go with it, hon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.52,0:17:44.73,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Great idea, Pinkie.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.73,0:17:46.94,Twilight,,0,0,0,,We'll be happy to help the yaks.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.94,0:17:49.17,Twilight,,0,0,0,,This is what friendship is all about.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.17,0:17:51.04,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Hey! I'll bring apples.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.04,0:17:53.65,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,This season's' batch are extra juicy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.65,0:17:57.48,Rarity,,0,0,0,,And I shall provide the yaks with Equestria's finest textiles.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.48,0:18:01.41,Rarity,,0,0,0,,They'll be silky and warm with hints of gold to complement their horns.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.41,0:18:02.31,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.55,0:18:05.48,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,We can't bring the yaks any pony stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.52,0:18:06.68,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.68,0:18:08.94,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,The yaks are very proud.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.94,0:18:10.74,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,They won't ask for help.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.74,0:18:11.94,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,You know what they say:
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.94,0:18:15.61,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,"You can lead a yak to water but you better no let him know you doing it"!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.92,0:18:17.99,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Nopony says that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.99,0:18:19.43,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Do they?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.83,0:18:20.72,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Okay then,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.81,0:18:23.71,Twilight,,0,0,0,,this will be unofficial cover friendship mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.90,0:18:24.65,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,You got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.21,0:18:27.10,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Is it yellow?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.10,0:18:28.14,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Is it slimy?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.14,0:18:29.37,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Is it slimy yellow?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.37,0:18:31.37,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,We're not playing that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.85,0:18:34.52,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,First!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.52,0:18:37.74,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,We have to infiltrate the yak camping.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.17,0:18:41.43,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,These walls are high.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.43,0:18:43.81,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Sneaking in will not be easy.
